        public ResultRange getPossibleResult(int dance,
                                     int competitor)
        Returns the possible result for a competitor in a specific dance.

        If the input is not set for the competitor, the range of all results still possible is beeing calculated.

        Parameters:
        dance - Index of the dance.
        competitor - Index of the competitor.
        Returns:
